se xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mdp1665702759283.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdp1665702759283.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mdp1665702759283.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mdp1665702759283\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Ends an XML element by adding the closing tag.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__topic_d136574e1_d136575e1_d136576e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__p_d136577e1_d136578e1_d136579e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ENDELEMENT()</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__section_xtc_qbh_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458859e59\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__p_d136721e1_d136722e1_d136723e1\">Values returned:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__ul_ltq_rbh_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__li_d48317e1_d48318e1_d48319e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> Success. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__li_d48320e1_d48321e1_d48322e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">–1</code> Failure. Called in an illegal\n               sequence. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__section_wvl_sbh_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d458859e81\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__p_d136589e1_d136590e1_d136591e1\">A call to the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ENDELEMENT</span>\n            operation is legal only after an invocation of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">STARTELEMENT</span> (to\n            immediately end the element just started), <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">CHARACTERS</span>,\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">ENDELEMENT</span> (to close both the nested and the parent element) or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DOCCOMMENT</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mdp1665702759283__p_d136592e1_d136593e1_d136594e1\">If the defined element is empty or has no text, it\n            is written as <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;ELEMENT/&gt;</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529868\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ENDELEMENT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Ends an XML element by adding the closing tag. ENDELEMENT() Return Values Values returned: 0 Success. –1 Failure. Called in an illegal sequence. Description A call to the ENDELEMENT operation is legal only after an invocation of STARTELEMENT (to immediately end the element just started), CHARACTERS , ENDELEMENT (to close both the nested and the parent element) or DOCCOMMENT . If the defined element is empty or has no text, it is written as <ELEMENT/> . Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}